SELECT b.* ,format_hn(visit.hn) as hn ,case when visit.fix_visit_type_id = '0' then format_vn(visit.vn) else format_an(visit.an) end as vn_an ,find_patient_name(visit.patient_id) as patient_name ,(b.percen_cost * b.discount) / 100 as discount_cost ,b.price_cost - ((b.percen_cost * b.discount) / 100) as price_net ,base_site_branch.description as site ,current_date as print_date ,current_time as print_time FROM ( SELECT a.* ,sum(receipt.cost :: float) as cost ,sum(receipt.discount :: float + receipt.decimal_discount :: float + receipt.special_discount :: float) as discount ,sum(receipt.paid :: float) as paid ,(a.price_cost / sum(receipt.cost :: float) ) * 100 as percen_cost FROM (
---ชุดตามผู้สั่ง select order_item.visit_id ,visit.visit_date ,order_item.order_item_id ,order_item.verify_date ,order_item.verify_time ,order_item.item_id ,item.common_name ,order_item.quantity --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_unit_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_billing_group_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,item.base_drug_type_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_cost :: float as item_cost ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_sale :: float as price_cost ,order_item.verify_spid ,base_department.base_department_id ,base_department.description as department from order_item inner join visit on order_item.visit_id = visit.visit_id inner join item on order_item.item_id = item.item_id left join base_service_point on order_item.verify_spid = base_service_point.base_service_point_id left join base_department on base_service_point.base_department_id = base_department.base_department_id where case when '$P!{xVn}' <> '' then visit.vn = substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),10,2)||substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),8,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),6,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),0,5) else visit.an = substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'1','2')||lpad(substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'3'),7,'0') end --visit.visit_id = '114011320525368501' and visit.financial_discharge = '1' and order_item.verify_eid <> 'imed' and item.fix_item_type_id <> '8' ---ตัดค่าอาหาร and base_service_point.base_department_id <> '' and order_item.verify_spid not in ('043','044','044.1','045','045.1','046','046.1','038','038.1','037.1','037','048.2','048.1','047','048','048.3','044.1.2.','042') ---ตัดรายการที่ห้องยา Lab Xray การเงิน สั่ง and order_item.verify_spid <> '068' --ตัดรายการ ICS สั่ง
UNION ALL
---ชุด Auto select a.* ,base_department.base_department_id ,base_department.description as department from ( select order_item.visit_id ,visit.visit_date ,order_item.order_item_id ,order_item.verify_date ,order_item.verify_time ,order_item.item_id ,item.common_name ,order_item.quantity --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_unit_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_billing_group_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,item.base_drug_type_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_cost :: float as item_cost ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_sale :: float as price_cost ,(select bed_management.base_service_point_id from visit inner join admit on visit.visit_id = admit.visit_id inner join bed_management on admit.admit_id = bed_management.admit_id where visit.visit_id = order_item.visit_id and (bed_management.move_date || bed_management.move_time) :: TEXT <= (order_item.verify_date || order_item.verify_time) :: TEXT order by bed_management.move_date DESC ,bed_management.move_time DESC limit 1) from order_item inner join item on order_item.item_id = item.item_id inner join visit on order_item.visit_id = visit.visit_id where case when '$P!{xVn}' <> '' then visit.vn = substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),10,2)||substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),8,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),6,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),0,5) else visit.an = substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'1','2')||lpad(substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'3'),7,'0') end --visit.visit_id = '114011320525368501' and visit.financial_discharge = '1' and order_item.verify_eid = 'imed' and order_item.fix_item_type_id <> '8' --ตัดค่าอาหาร )a left join base_service_point on a.base_service_point_id = base_service_point.base_service_point_id left join base_department on base_service_point.base_department_id = base_department.base_department_id
UNION ALL
---ชุด โภชนา select order_item.visit_id ,visit.visit_date ,order_item.order_item_id ,order_item.verify_date ,order_item.verify_time ,order_item.item_id ,item.common_name ,order_item.quantity --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_unit_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_billing_group_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,item.base_drug_type_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_cost :: float as item_cost ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_sale :: float as price_cost ,'061' as verify_spid ,'B0005' as base_department_id ,'แผนกโภชนาการ' as department from order_item inner join item on order_item.item_id = item.item_id inner join visit on order_item.visit_id = visit.visit_id where case when '$P!{xVn}' <> '' then visit.vn = substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),10,2)||substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),8,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),6,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),0,5) else visit.an = substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'1','2')||lpad(substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'3'),7,'0') end --visit.visit_id = '114011320525368501' and visit.financial_discharge = '1' and order_item.fix_item_type_id = '8'

--ชุด ICS Fl.3 select order_item.visit_id ,visit.visit_date ,order_item.order_item_id ,order_item.verify_date ,order_item.verify_time ,order_item.item_id ,item.common_name ,order_item.quantity --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_unit_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.base_billing_group_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,item.base_drug_type_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_cost :: float as item_cost ,order_item.quantity :: float * order_item.unit_price_sale :: float as price_cost ,'003' as verify_spid ,'F0031' as base_department_id ,'แผนกตรวจสุขภาพ' as department from order_item inner join item on order_item.item_id = item.item_id inner join visit on order_item.visit_id = visit.visit_id where case when '$P!{xVn}' <> '' then visit.vn = substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),10,2)||substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),8,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),6,2) || substr(lpad('$P!{xVn}',11,'0'),0,5) else visit.an = substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'1','2')||lpad(substr(replace('$P!{xAn}','/',''),'3'),7,'0') end and order_item.verify_spid = '068' and visit.financial_discharge = '1' and order_item.fix_item_type_id <> '8'
)a inner join receipt on a.visit_id = receipt.visit_id where receipt.fix_receipt_type_id in ('1','7') and receipt.fix_receipt_status_id = '2' and receipt.patient_id not in ('157416','218472')
GROUP BY a.visit_id ,a.visit_date ,a.order_item_id ,a.verify_date ,a.verify_time ,a.item_id ,a.common_name ,a.quantity --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,a.base_unit_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,a.base_billing_group_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,a.base_drug_type_id --ธีรศักดิ์ ถูกใจ เพิ่มตรงนี้ ,a.item_cost ,a.price_cost ,a.verify_spid ,a.base_department_id ,a.department )b inner join visit on b.visit_id = visit.visit_id inner join base_service_point on b.verify_spid = base_service_point.base_service_point_id inner join base_site_branch on base_service_point.base_site_branch_id = base_site_branch.base_site_branch_id ORDER BY b.department,b.verify_date
